data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Old Palm Valley community in Ponte Vedra Beach. This Classic brick home sits in a quaint cul-de-sac where children can safely play & neighbors become friends. Enjoy your private pool & spa in your secluded backyard that is perfect for creating cherished memories. The Master Bedroom, 2 Guest Bedrooms & an Office downstairs provide ample space for family & friends. The upstairs versatile bonus room can be tailored to your needs with a full bathroom & closet. Rich warm hardwood floors, a wood burning fireplace & crown molding are the ideal blend of modern & timeless charm. With its prime location, you'll have easy access to pristine beaches & a community that's renowned for its top-quality schools. Are you ready to call this home?
